	(202, 421, 'zhCN', '', 'Sha\'naar Temple', 'In the hills of the Tanaan jungle is an ancient temple. Once it was a holy place, but now the sargerei turned it into their nativity scene - they call demons there.\r\n\r\nWe must strike them before they finish their rituals. The longer we drag with this, the stronger the enemy will be.', '', 0),
	(202, 422, 'zhCN', '', 'Tron Kiel\'ed', 'The Shadow Council summons its demon lords on the mountain they call the Throne of Kil\'jaeden. Without a doubt, this is the most dangerous region in all of Tanaan.\r\n\r\nSo gather a squad of strong fighters and attack the Throne of Kil\'jaeden, before the Legion has had time to gain a foothold there!\r\n\r\n| cFF7a0000 [Task for the group] | r', '', 0),
	(192, 401, 'zhCN', '', 'Iron Fortress Harbor', 'The Iron Horde continues to collect remnants of its forces from all over Draenor. If we allow them to continue to receive reinforcements and supplies without hindrance, our positions in Tanaan will weaken very quickly.\r\n\r\nHaving dealt a strategic blow to their supply routes in the harbor of the Iron Fortress, we will force the enemy to go on the defensive and retain the initiative.', '', 0),
	(192, 402, 'zhCN', '', 'Fel Forge', 'Gul\'dan\'s minions enhance the Iron Horde war machines with fel magic. Scouts even report on the construction of a felbot!\r\n\r\nFight in the Fel Forge and destroy these infernal machines before there are too many of them.', '', 0),
	(204, 425, 'zhCN', '', 'Zet\'Gol', 'The Blood-Eye Clan continues to pose a serious threat. In Zet\'Gol, they constantly chase our scouts, interfere with operations and collect resources for Gul\'dan\'s dark magic.\r\n\r\nWe need to organize a raid on Zet\'Gol so that they pull their forces, dispersed throughout the valley, to one point. This will untie our hands at least for a while.', '', 0),
	(204, 426, 'zhCN', '', 'Fel Forge', 'Gul\'dan\'s minions enhance the Iron Horde war machines with fel magic. Scouts even report on the construction of a felbot!\r\n\r\nFight in the Fel Forge and destroy these infernal machines before there are too many of them.', '', 0),
	(253, 541, 'zhCN', '鲜血', '选择', '裂肉者高瑞里克斯是一名凶残而庞大的恶魔战士。他挥舞着他的巨斧诅咒之喉，为军团屠戮了许多个世界。\n\n要想从高瑞里克斯那里夺取这把强大的武器，你需要只身前往入侵我们世界的军团部队的核心地带。但诅咒之喉中蕴含的力量会让你的冒险得到回报。', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(253, 542, 'zhCN', '冰霜', '选择', '传奇武器霜之哀伤于四年前在冰冠堡被毁，即便如此，它依然还是艾泽拉斯最恶名昭彰的武器之一。\n\n只需要用上一点死灵法术，它的碎片便可被重铸为一对符文剑，其潜力绝不会逊色于霜之哀伤，甚至可能比霜之哀伤更加强大。', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(253, 543, 'zhCN', '邪恶', '选择', '天启是一把由纳斯雷兹姆所铸造的古剑，它曾散播过无数的瘟疫、死亡和恐慌，乃是究极的毁灭利器。\n\n这把剑曾由提瑞斯秘法会所使用，但后来被黑暗骑士夺走。若想要把它找回来，我们必须前往黑暗骑士的秘密巢穴。', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(242, 511, 'zhCN', '酒仙', '选择', '我们从传说中了解到，很久之前曾经有一把法杖，是用潘达利亚第一棵树木的枝条制成的。\n\n据说持有这把法杖的人不会被任何武器伤害到。\n\n传说中还说，最后一个拥有这把法杖的人是美猴王。要想找到它，我们应该从美猴王开始求索。', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(242, 512, 'zhCN', '织雾', '选择', '很久以前，熊猫人的末代皇帝使用他的法杖“神龙”将潘达利亚笼罩在了迷雾之中。\n\n法杖在永春台保留了数个世代。当军团攻打潘达利亚时，影踪派的守军们立刻前去保护法杖。但他们一去就没了音讯，事态恐怕不妙了——我们绝不能让法杖落入坏人手里！', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(242, 513, 'zhCN', '踏风', '选择', '云游四海的冒险者们回到岛上后流传着一个有趣的故事。他们提到一对古老的拳刃，据说能赐给持有者风暴之力。\n\n我们对这对神秘的兵器知之甚少，但假如它们真有那样的力量，那我们应该试着去寻找一下。', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(248, 532, 'zhCN', '神圣', '选择', '为了躲避军团的追捕，德莱尼曾在多个星球上辗转逃难。在其中一颗星球上，一群勇士带着治愈水晶图雷勇敢地对抗燃烧军团，使他们的同胞得以逃脱。\n\n最近有传言说，达拉然中的一名士兵曾在军团手中目击到了这颗水晶。如果消息是真的，我们必须把它夺回来！', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(248, 533, 'zhCN', '暗影', '选择', '一把上古之神的匕首最近重现人间，暮光之锤意图利用它来东山再起。他们正用那匕首执行一个邪恶的仪式，我们必须阻止它。\n\n黑暗帝国之刃曾在已被忘却的时代被用于执行和上古之神有关的邪恶仪式。这把仪祭刀能与虚空共鸣，并能使用强大的暗影能量来强化它的主人。', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(248, 534, 'zhCN', '戒律', '选择', '血色十字军对消灭艾泽拉斯亡灵的执着近乎狂热，他们曾试图以法杖的形式打造出第二件灰烬使者级别的神器。 然而，仪式遭到了叛徒的破坏，还引发了剧烈的爆炸。这把受损的法杖释放出的力量几乎无法驾驭。\n\n最后，肯瑞托的精英法师将此杖藏在了安全的地方，以免引发更多的灾难。', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(280, 621, 'zhCN', 'Outlaw', 'Select', 'The creepy admiral Eliza is a thunderstorm in the South Seas. Her cursed blades scare many.\r\n\r\nWe learned that her ship anchored off the coast of Azsuna on the Broken Isles. If you hurry, you can get her blades.', '', 0),
	(280, 622, 'zhCN', 'Stealth', 'Select', 'Akaari Blood Darkness is an unsurpassed Eredar assassin, a subject of special pride of the Legion. Her daggers can distort space, hiding its owner in the shade.\r\n\r\nWe have intelligence data indicating where it is currently located. It\'s time to strike.', '', 0),
	(270, 594, 'zhCN', 'Secret magic', 'Select', 'The most famous owner of Alunet is Aegwynn, the only woman among the Keepers of Tirisfal, although, apparently, the artifact is much older than her.\r\n\r\nWhen her life was drawing to a close, Aegwynne handed the staff to the blue dragons. They found the artifact too dangerous and locked it in a secret vault, where it is to this day.', '', 0),
	(270, 595, 'zhCN', 'Fire', 'Select', 'Felo\'melorn, in the translation “Blow of Fire”, once glittered in the hands of warriors from the clan of the Solar Wanderers, who valiantly fought in the War of the Ancient and Troll Wars and opposed the death knight Arthas Menethil.\r\n\r\nIn the end, the sword was lost in the icy wastes of Northrend.', '', 0),
	(164, 345, 'zhCN', '', 'Broken Precipice', 'Massive ogron have been battering our frontlines, and no matter how many we down, there seem to be more to replace them.\n\nMost of these ogron appear to be coming from the Broken Precipice, deep in western Nagrand. If we\'re to stand a chance in the coming battles, we need to find a way to remove these ogron from the battlefield.', '', 0),
	(164, 346, 'zhCN', '', 'The Pit (Group)', 'The Blackrock forces based out of the Pit in Gorgrond make up the bulk of the Iron Horde army. If we crush them on their home soil, the rest of the Iron Horde will have little hope of standing against us.\n\nIf you choose the battle, bring friends. The Blackrock won\'t be defeated easily.', '', 0),
	(284, 633, 'zhCN', 'Secret magic', 'Select', 'The most famous owner of Alunet is Aegwynn, the only woman among the Keepers of Tirisfal, although, apparently, the artifact is much older than her.\r\n\r\nWhen her life was drawing to a close, Aegwynne handed the staff to the blue dragons. They found the artifact too dangerous and locked it in a secret vault, where it is to this day.', '', 0),
	(284, 635, 'zhCN', 'Ice', 'Select', 'This staff belonged to Alodi, the first Guardian of Tirisfal. The staff went through many battles against the Legion with the owner over the century when he wore his honorary title.\r\n\r\nMoving away from business, Alodi disappeared and carried the staff with him. What happened to them later, no one knows - except, perhaps, Alodi himself.', '', 0),
	(287, 644, 'zhCN', 'Stealth', 'Select', 'Akaari Blood Darkness is an unsurpassed Eredar assassin, a subject of special pride of the Legion. Her daggers can distort space, hiding its owner in the shade.\r\n\r\nWe have intelligence data indicating where it is currently located. It\'s time to strike.', '', 0),
	(274, 601, 'zhCN', 'Improvement', 'Select', 'Doomhammer sunk into the Maelstrom. Care must be taken that he does not fall into the wrong hands.\r\n\r\nMy husband Go\'el, whom you call Thrall, has already gone to the Underdark to track him down. Beware: Get\'zun’s demon was also dragged into the Maelstrom, and he may still be alive.', '', 0),
	(274, 602, 'zhCN', 'Elements', 'Select', 'Gladiator Regar is aware of powerful weapons that can help us confront the Legion.\r\n\r\nAfter the Pandaren campaign under the Throne of Thunder, the weapons of the storm god Ra-den were discovered. He was left under the protection of the followers of the White Tiger with the order to give only the most worthy. Regar will help you prove your right to it.', '', 0),
	(292, 658, 'zhCN', 'Darkness', 'Select', 'The Twilight\'s Hammer cult wants to regain its former power: it conducts a ritual in which the once lost dagger of the Old Gods surfaced. This unholy ritual must be stopped.\r\n\r\nThe blade of the Dark Empire is a dagger for sacrifice, enchanted by the energy of the Abyss. It was used in terrifying rituals dedicated to the Ancient Gods, from time immemorial. The dagger saturates its owner with the powerful energy of darkness.', '', 0),
	(273, 599, 'zhCN', 'Darkness', 'Select', 'The Twilight\'s Hammer cult wants to regain its former power: it conducts a ritual in which the once lost dagger of the Old Gods surfaced. This unholy ritual must be stopped.\r\n\r\nThe blade of the Dark Empire is a dagger for sacrifice, enchanted by the energy of the Abyss. It was used in terrifying rituals dedicated to the Ancient Gods, from time immemorial. The dagger saturates its owner with the powerful energy of darkness.', '', 0),
	(273, 598, 'zhCN', 'Shine', 'Select', 'The Draenei had to flee many worlds, fleeing the pursuit of the Legion. In one of these worlds, some of the bravest remained to detain the demons and give the rest time to leave, and they had a shining healing stone - T\'uure.\r\n\r\nRumor has it that in Dalaran a warrior saw a missing crystal in the hands of demons. If true, you need to get it.', '', 0),
	(273, 600, 'zhCN', 'Obedience', 'Select', 'The scarlet order, obsessed with the idea of ​​cleansing Azeroth from the undead, tried to create a staff - the likeness of the Incinerator. However, a scout from the Legion, who entered the order, intervened in the creation ritual - and it all ended in a powerful fiery explosion. The strength of the damaged staff was almost impossible to control.\r\n\r\nFearing destruction and chaos, the high magicians of the Kirin Tor hid the staff where no one could find it.', '', 0),
	(279, 617, 'zhCN', 'Witchcraft', 'Select', 'The reaper of the Dead Wind once belonged to the first of the necrolytes, Satael, and at one time destroyed all life on the pass of the Dead Wind. For many centuries, he was lost sight of, but recently it turned out that Ulthales is in the hands of the Dark Riders. You need to track them down to find out where they hid the artifact.', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(279, 618, 'zhCN', 'Demonology', 'Select', 'Sorcerer Tal\'kiel was one of the first eredars to master the technique of summoning and controlling demons.\r\nWhen he was defeated, his skull was put on public display as a reminder of how dangerous dark art is.\r\nBut this lesson has not been learned.\r\n\r\nAfter the fall of the Eredar, the commanders of the Burning Legion took the skull to strengthen control over their troops.', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(282, 626, 'zhCN', 'Balance', 'Select', 'The spit of Elune, kept by Tyrande, the High Priestess of Elune, is known among the Druids for its long and controversial history.\r\n\r\nThe artifact is associated with the origin of the worgen and, as they say, has an unimaginable lunar power, which only the most skilled of the druids can curb.\r\n\r\nWe need to convince Tyrande and her people that the Scythe can be trusted with you.', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(282, 628, 'zhCN', 'Watchman', 'Select', 'The mighty bear god Ursoc died during the War of the Ancients, protecting Azeroth from the Burning Legion.\r\n\r\nHis claws, once terrifying enemies, are now kept in the Emerald Dream, and the spirit of Ursoc protects them.\r\n\r\nIf you can get the Claws, they will greatly help us in the fight against the Legion.', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(282, 629, 'zhCN', 'Healing', 'Select', 'Many thousands of years ago, Aviana presented the first druids with a branch of G\'Hanir, the Primordial Tree.\r\n\r\nThe branch has become a staff that is said to help its owner achieve perfect harmony with nature and learn very powerful healing spells.\r\n\r\nThe artifact is stored in the sanctuary under the roots of Chaladrassil, but not so long ago, communication with the local druids was lost.', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(275, 605, 'zhCN', 'Protection', 'Select', 'Once, the ancient king of vrykul managed to get the scales of the Earth Keeper Neltharion and make of it a shield of unprecedented power. This shield now rests next to its creator in a forgotten tomb.\r\n\r\nGet this shield and you will get not only impenetrable protection, but also a particle of fiery power of one of the Aspects.', '', 0),
	(275, 606, 'zhCN', 'Fury', 'Select', 'The battle swords of the Valariars, the greatest of my defenders, were stolen by this damned Helia. She and her foolish servant taunt the heroes, abducting their souls before they can ascend to the Halls of Valor.\r\n\r\nWith this powerful weapon in battle, you will become like a storm of steel and fire. Better and can not be desired.', '', 0),
	(277, 610, 'zhCN', 'Khmelevar', 'Select', 'Legends tell of a staff that was made of the first tree grown on the land of Pandaria.\r\n\r\nThe one who owns this staff, as if he could not hit a single weapon.\r\n\r\nThe last known owner was the Monkey King. With him we should begin the search.', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(277, 611, 'zhCN', 'Weaver of fog', 'Select', 'Once upon a time, the last Pandaren emperor with the help of Shey-moon, his staff, covered the whole country with fogs.\r\n\r\nFor many generations the staff was kept on the Terrace of Eternal Spring. When the Legion attacked Pandaria, the Shado-Pan defenders rushed there. Since then there has been no news from them, and we fear the worst. The staff should not go to the enemy!', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(288, 645, 'zhCN', 'Extermination', 'Select', 'These twin blades belong to the former demon hunter Varedis the Corrupted Soul, who died many years ago defending the Black Temple.\r\n\r\nLord of the Burning Legion Kil\'jaeden the Tempter returned Varedis from the Twisting Nether and filled his glaives with his chaotic power.', '', 0),
	(274, 603, 'zhCN', 'Healing', 'Select', 'It is said that Queen Azshara had a scepter that allowed her to command the seas and waters of life.\r\n\r\nErunak had long tried to find out his whereabouts, and one of his shamans almost succeeded, but she disappeared. Did her searches succeed? Can legends turn out to be true? And what can this artifact be capable of in the hands of a talented shaman?', '', 0),
	(245, 523, 'zhCN', '痛苦', '选择', '逆风收割者是最初的通灵师萨泰尔的武器，它抽干了逆风小径所有的生命，并以此得名。\n\n在失踪了数个世纪后，我们最终查明，乌萨勒斯落入了黑暗骑士的手中。你若想找到这件神器，就必须去追踪那些黑暗骑士了。', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(237, 495, 'zhCN', '', 'Here is my choice.', 'Choose this option if you want to learn how to cut |cFF1EFF00|Hitem130216:0:0:0:0:0:0:0:90:0|h[boost speed]|h|r,which increases your speed indicator.', '', 0),
	(237, 494, 'zhCN', '', 'Here is my choice.', 'Choose this option if you want to learn how to cut |cFF1EFF00|Hitem:130215:0:0:0:0:0:0:0:90:0|h[deadly dark amber]|h|r, which increases your critical strike damage .', '', 0),
	(237, 496, 'zhCN', '', 'Here is my choice.', 'Choose this option if you want to learn how to cut |cFF1EFF00|Hitem:130218:0:0:0:0:0:0:0:90:0|h[deadly dark amber]|h|r, which increases your skill.', '', 0),
	(238, 498, 'zhCN', '', 'Here is my choice.', 'Choose this option if you want to learn how to create |cFF0070DD|Hitem:130223:0:0:0:0:0:0:0:90:0|h[dark amber ring]|h|r, which increases your critical strike .', '', 0),
	(238, 499, 'zhCN', '', 'Here is my choice.', 'Choose this option if you want to learn how to create |cFF0070DD|Hitem:130225:0:0:0:0:0:0:0:90:0|h[azsunite ring]|h|r, which increases your speed indicator.', '', 0),
	(238, 497, 'zhCN', '', 'Here is my choice.', 'Choose this option if you want to learn how to create |cFF0070DD|Hitem:130224:0:0:0:0:0:0:0:90:0|h[a ring with a heavenly stone]|h|r, which increases your universality index.', '', 0),
	(246, 527, 'zhCN', '', 'Here is my choice.', 'Choose this option if you want to learn how to create |cFF0070DD|Hitem:130220:0:0:0:0:0:0:0:90:0|h[fast light]|h|r, which increases your speed indicator.', '', 0),
	(246, 526, 'zhCN', '', 'Here is my choice.', 'Choose this option if you want to learn how to create |cFF0070DD|Hitem:130219:0:0:0:0:0:0:0:90:0|h[the deadly eye of the Prophecy]|h|r, which increases your critical strike damage .', '', 0),
	(246, 528, 'zhCN', '', 'Here is my choice.', 'Choose this option if you want to learn how to create |cFF0070DD|Hitem:130220:0:0:0:0:0:0:0:90:0|h[dark mastery ruby]|h|r, which increases your skill indicator.', '', 0),
	(247, 545, 'zhCN', '恢复', '选择', '数千年前，艾维娜将母亲之树加尼尔的一根枝条赐给了最初的德鲁伊们。\n\n据说这把法杖可以让持有者与自然达到完美的和谐，能够使用最强大的恢复法术。\n\n这跟枝条被保管在莎拉达希尔下方的祭坛中，但最近有情报显示它和那里的德鲁伊一块失踪了……', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(240, 504, 'zhCN', '野兽控制', '选择', '在远古时代，曾有一名维库督军偷得了一把灌注有风暴之力的步枪。他使用这件神器的力量征服了破碎群岛上的敌人。\n\n进入这名督军的墓穴，取得这件强大的武器。', 'CONFIRM_ARTIFACT_CHOICE', 0),
	(87, 192, 'zhCN', '', 'Shattrath (group)', 'Every day, the Sargerai troops in Shattrath are becoming stronger and bolder. They pose a serious threat and can no longer be ignored.\r\n\r\nGather allies if you want to launch an attack on the Sargerais who took refuge in the city.', '', 26365),
	(87, 191, 'zhCN', '', 'Plateau of the Secretary', 'Recent reports indicate increased activity of the Sargerai troops on the Socretar Plateau in the Shadowmoon Valley.\r\n\r\nSocrethar\'s minions present a danger to both the draenei and our garrison. You need to deal with them as soon as possible.', '', 26365),
	(352, 997, 'zhCN', 'Gorgrond', 'Go to Gorgrond', 'The Blackrock Orcs are great masters in working with Blackrock ore, from which they smelter guns for the artillery and fleet of the Iron Horde.\r\n\r\nSet up a base in Gorgrond and stop the Iron Horde\'s mechanical battalion, terrifying Draenor.', '', 26365),
	(308, 753, 'zhCN', '夜之子', '选择', '在保护屏障下与世隔绝地生活了一万年后，苏拉玛的精灵越来越依赖暗夜井的奥术魔力。为了保护这座力量之泉，夜之子的领袖们与燃烧军团达成了协议，但却使自己的王国陷入了内战。从他们的恶魔主子手中夺回自由后，夜之子需要盟友来帮助他们找回自己在这个世界的位置。', 'CONFIRM_ALLY_CHOICE', 26654),
	(308, 752, 'zhCN', '至高岭牛头人', '选择', '作为上古之战的英雄胡恩的后裔，至高岭牛头人崇拜大地、河流与天空之灵。虽然燃烧军团入侵了他们的土地，并在部族间种下了纷争的种子，但高岭诸族还是再次团结到了一起。现在，他们终于做好了准备，走出圣山，与他们来自卡利姆多的同胞并肩战斗，将他们的高尚品格和惊人力量带到强大的部落。', 'CONFIRM_ALLY_CHOICE', 26654),
	(322, 783, 'zhCN', '虚空精灵', '选择', '许多人都曾试图掌握虚空的堕落魔力。大部分这么做的人最终都陷入了疯狂。决心使用这种力量为艾泽拉斯的福祉而战的奥蕾莉亚·风行者，成为了第一个成功抗拒暗影低语的凡人。为了帮助一群几乎堕入黑暗的同胞，奥蕾莉亚发誓要教导这些虚空精灵控制体内的暗影，并让他们用这种新获得的力量为联盟效力。', 'CONFIRM_ALLY_CHOICE', 26755),
	(322, 784, 'zhCN', '光铸德莱尼', '选择', '圣光军团与燃烧军团在扭曲虚空中厮杀了数千年。舍身投入这场漫长远征的德莱尼会接受仪式，将圣光的精华注入体内，成为光铸者。在阿古斯之战获得最终的胜利后，光铸者有了一个新的任务：保护艾泽拉斯不受任何威胁，并帮助联盟击退部落的入侵。', 'CONFIRM_ALLY_CHOICE', 26822),
	(317, 776, 'zhCN', '回响遮罩', '选择', '选择后可以在阿古斯使用奥术回响遮罩的隐形能力。', '', 27602),
	(317, 775, 'zhCN', '邪能之心', '选择', '选择阿古斯邪能之心可以让你在阿古斯受到致命伤害后复活，并在非战斗状态下持续为你恢复生命值。', '', 27602),
	(317, 771, 'zhCN', '圣光裁决者', '选择', '选择后可以在阿古斯使用维迪卡尔的主武器圣光裁决者瞄准并轰炸目标。', '', 27602),
	(317, 782, 'zhCN', '', '激活', '激活矩阵核心，选择维迪卡尔的主武器圣光裁决者作为你在阿古斯的能力。', '', 27602),
	(317, 774, 'zhCN', '战争机甲', '选择', '选择后可以在阿古斯使用光铸战争机甲。', '', 27602),
	(70, 158, 'zhCN', '', 'Pit (group)', 'The forces of the Blackrock clan, based in the Pit area of ​​Gorgrond, form the backbone of the Iron Horde army. If we smash them in their native land, the remnants of the Iron Horde will no longer be able to withstand us.\r\n\r\nIf you decide on this battle, take reliable comrades with you. It’s definitely not worth counting on an easy victory over the Black Mountain clan.', '', 25961),
	(70, 157, 'zhCN', '', 'Plateau of the Secretary', 'Recent reports indicate increased activity of the Sargerai troops on the Socretar Plateau in the Shadowmoon Valley.\r\n\r\nSocrethar\'s minions present a danger to both the draenei and our garrison. You need to deal with them as soon as possible.', '', 25961);
